text: I recently started my first real data science project since I always practice projects using hands on projects on youtube and work step by step with the youtuber. I asked a mentor to guide me and I found this project is wayyyyy complicated and advanced for me..mind you this is supposed to be a begginer friendly project...if anyone can assist me I would really appreciate it. I only have kaggle Certifications ...also let's connect on linkedin..would love to learn from everyone
